<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-soloUnRelojEnLaPared" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>Sample response: I agree with Lin. The hour hand is between 1 and 2, so the hour is 1. The minute hand is not at the 7. It is 2 of the little tick marks past the 7. The minute hand would be at the 7 if it were 1:35, so it's 2 more minutes to where the minute hand is.</p></li>
      <li><ol>
<li>1:09</li>
<li>11:11</li>
<li>8:37</li>
<li>7:58</li>
</ol>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


